dane <- get_eurostat(id = 'isoc_ci_ifp_iu', type = 'label')

Table  isoc_ci_ifp_iu  read from cache file:  /var/folders/zs/2z4rlxv54pv7ml4jld2kccmc0000gn/T//RtmpfQtNe9/eurostat/isoc_ci_ifp_iu_date_label_FF.rds
head(dane)
dane %>% 
  mutate(eu = countrycode(geo, origin = "country.name", destination = "eu28")) %>%
  filter(!is.na(eu)) %>%
  filter(indic_is == 'Last internet use: in last 3 months' , 
         year(time) %in% 2005:2020,
         #geo %in% c('Poland', "Czechia", "Hungary", "Slovakia", "Slovenia"),
         ind_type %in% c('All Individuals', 'Individuals, 16 to 24 years old',
           'Individuals, 25 to 34 years old',
           'Individuals, 35 to 44 years old',
           'Individuals, 45 to 54 years old',
           'Individuals, 55 to 74 years old'),
         unit == 'Percentage of individuals') %>%
  mutate(ind_type = case_when(ind_type == "All Individuals"  ~ "Ogem",
            ind_type ==  "Individuals, 16 to 24 years old" ~ "16-24",
            ind_type ==  "Individuals, 25 to 34 years old" ~ "25-34",
            ind_type ==  "Individuals, 35 to 44 years old" ~ "35-44",
            ind_type ==  "Individuals, 45 to 54 years old" ~ "45-54",
            ind_type ==  "Individuals, 55 to 74 years old" ~ "55-74"),
         ind_type = factor(ind_type, levels = c("Ogem", "16-24", "25-34", "35-44", "45-54", "55-74"), 
                           ordered = TRUE)) %>%
  select(ind_type, time, values, geo) %>%
  ggplot(data = .,
         aes(x = time,
             y = values,
             group = geo)) + 
  geom_line() +
  gghighlight(geo %in% c("Poland"), 
              calculate_per_facet = TRUE, 
               label_params = list(fill = NA)) + 
  xlab('Okres badania') +
  ylab('Odsetek osb') +
  scale_colour_brewer(name = 'Przekrj', palette = 'Set1') +
  ggtitle('Odsetek korzystajcych z Internetu w ostatnich 3 miesicach w Polsce i UE') +
  facet_wrap(~ind_type)  -> p

dane %>% 
  mutate(eu = countrycode(geo, origin = "country.name", destination = "eu28")) %>%
  filter(!is.na(eu)) %>%
  filter(indic_is == 'Last internet use: in last 3 months' , 
         year(time) %in% 2005:2020,
         geo %in% c('Poland', "Estonia", "Netherlands", "France", "Italy", "Spain", "Finland"),
         ind_type %in% c('All Individuals', 'Individuals, 16 to 24 years old',
           'Individuals, 25 to 34 years old',
           'Individuals, 35 to 44 years old',
           'Individuals, 45 to 54 years old',
           'Individuals, 55 to 74 years old'),
         unit == 'Percentage of individuals') %>%
  mutate(ind_type = case_when(ind_type == "All Individuals"  ~ "Ogem",
            ind_type ==  "Individuals, 16 to 24 years old" ~ "16-24",
            ind_type ==  "Individuals, 25 to 34 years old" ~ "25-34",
            ind_type ==  "Individuals, 35 to 44 years old" ~ "35-44",
            ind_type ==  "Individuals, 45 to 54 years old" ~ "45-54",
            ind_type ==  "Individuals, 55 to 74 years old" ~ "55-74"),
         ind_type = factor(ind_type, levels = c("Ogem", "16-24", "25-34", "35-44", "45-54", "55-74"), 
                           ordered = TRUE)) %>%
  select(ind_type, time, values, geo) %>%
  ggplot(data = .,
         aes(x = time,
             y = values,
             group = geo,
             color = geo)) + 
  geom_line() +
  xlab('Okres badania') +
  ylab('Odsetek osb') +
  scale_colour_brewer(name = 'Przekrj', palette = 'Paired') +
  ggtitle('Odsetek korzystajcych z Internetu w ostatnich 3 miesicach w Polsce i wybrane kraje') +
  facet_wrap(~ind_type)  -> p
